com.sun.javatest

Class TestFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.javatest.TestFilter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AllTestsFilter, CompositeFilter, ExcludeListFilter, InitialUrlFilter, KeywordsFilter, ObservableTestFilter, StatusFilter

    public abstract class TestFilter
extends java.lang.Object
    A filter interface for TestDescriptions. Implementations of this class should implement the equals() and hashCode() as per the spec in java.lang.Object. This is used by the harness for file equality purposes which looking for changes and optimizations to perform.
    See Also:
    TestDescription
